{"TopicId":103503,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Kerbol keeps ruining my screenshot.","CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T06:41:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T06:41:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo I\u0027m trying to get a nice picture, but the sun is in the background and it makes everything else too dark to see. Suggestions?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/5F7u6t8.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00225F7u6t8.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E/troll\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zucal","CreatedById":139764,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T06:42:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust look on the bright side!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T07:01:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHave you tried turning it off?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rabada","CreatedById":66044,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T07:28:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RainDreamer\u0022 data-cite=\u0022RainDreamer\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHave you tried turning it off?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EReally he should only try to take these pictures at night... Everyone knows that is the best time to land on the sun.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOP, perhaps you could try the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/71536-0-90-0-Ambient-Light-Adjustment-1-3-1-1-20-12-14-%28continued%29\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eambient light adjustment mod\u003C/a\u003E? Normally it is used to make the game brighter when your craft are in Kerbin\u0027s shadow, but I just checked it and it also can make the game slightly darker.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kruleworld","CreatedById":69697,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T09:58:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E...but that\u0027s such a COOL screenshot...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T10:52:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou are obviously going too slow. 90405 m/s is just 0.03 % of the speed of light - therefore you are only emitting 0.03 % of the light you could, and the light from Kerbol is overpowering yours. Try accelerating a lot and show the damn star who\u0027s boss.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i2.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/170/391/1315085019001.png\u0022 alt=\u00221315085019001.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SRV Ron","CreatedById":69806,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T11:00:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENeeds to get much closer to his subject. And, you can\u0027t get much details anyways when you take your picture directly into the sun, even the Kerbal one.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/q6DqCF4.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022q6DqCF4.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T15:13:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EXD kerbol every time why you got to be so bright \u002Brep for making me laugh\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Destroyer713","CreatedById":136956,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T15:18:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHave you tried unplugging the sun?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Windspren","CreatedById":134441,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T16:08:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDump some water on it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fleb","CreatedById":63851,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T19:11:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laythe Dweller\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Laythe Dweller\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EDump some water on it!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECrash Eeloo into it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Daze","CreatedById":57997,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T19:33:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fleb\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Fleb\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ECrash Eeloo into it!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMinmus for a flavoured mint mousse\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr_Brain","CreatedById":33487,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T22:08:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust set the sun on fire. Once it\u0027s burned down, it\u0027s not there anymore, so it can\u0027t bother you anymore.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T00:15:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for all the informative responses!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHowever, I must inform you all that this was a ruse to trick you all into looking directly into the sun!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESuckers. I\u0027m telling your moms.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"quietsamurai98","CreatedById":69270,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T02:01:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laythe Dweller\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Laythe Dweller\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EDump some water on it!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://what-if.xkcd.com/14/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://what-if.xkcd.com/14/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T02:54:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOk, back up a little,,, a little bit more,,, a little bit more,,, BACK UP!!!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RW-1","CreatedById":107278,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-08T19:13:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESurprised no one said it yet - Take it at Night .... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/defa